h2 Examples
p.-text
  | To display a card, use the class <code>a-card</code>.

h3 Base
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    .a-card(style="width:20rem;")
      .a-card__content.-text
        | This is a card
  :code(lang="html")
    <div class="a-card">
      <div class="a-card__content">
        This is a card
      </div>
    </div>

